{
  "texts": [
    "In order to give the generator more direct supervision, a feature-aware loss that makes use of the visualization of the characteristics supplied by the self-supervised discriminator was also implemented.",
    "In accordance with the findings of the experiments undertaken on the MS-COCO collection, the suggested methodology resulted in a significant increase to the state-of-the-art FID score, which dropped from 28.92 to 24.58.Novel convolutional recurrent GAN (CRGAN) architectures for voice improvement were proposed by Li et al.",
    "In order to allow for comparing the differences with other GANbased systems, multiple loss functions were implemented.",
    "Recurrent layer advantages were also investigated.",
    "The outcomes of the studies substantiated the appropriateness of the postulated CRGAN model outperformed other non-GAN based systems and the SOTA GANbased models using the identical loss functions, demonstrating the advantages of using a GAN for voice augmentation.To create images from vocal communications, Zhang et al. [79] used a GAN technique that included spectral norm, projection discriminator, and auxiliary classifier as opposed to naïve conditional GAN."
  ]
}